Package: shinyChromosomeR
Type: Package
Title: the R package for shinyChromosome, an Shiny application for interactive creation of non-circular whole genome diagram
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2019-05-27
Author: Yiming Yu and Wen Yao
Maintainer: Yiming Yu <yimingyyu@gmail.com>
Description: shinyChromosome is an Shiny application for interactive creation of non-circular plots of whole genomes using the web browser. shinyChromosomeR wraps the core script of shinyChromosome as an R package, allowing the creation of non-circular whole genome diagram from the R command line.
License: Artistic-2.0
LazyData: TRUE
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0), plyr, ggplot2, RColorBrewer, ggthemes
Imports: reshape2
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests: knitr
